product_description.Dedicated 3-Card Slot: Thanks to the 2 SIM card slots and a microSD card slot on this realme C35 mobile phone, you can enjoy blazing-fast network connectivity as well as massive storage.
product_description.18W Fast Charging: The 18W power adapter enhances the battery life of this smartphone within a short time, thus allowing you to enjoy your phone throughout the day.
product_description.Capture Clear Photos with AI Triple Came: The 50 MP AI Triple Camera of this realme C35 smartphone comes equipped with 3 specially designed lenses that allow you to experiment with photography for capturing clear images.
product_description.Monstrous Battery: This mobile phone runs on a massive 5000 mAh battery that keeps your phone powered throughout the day. Also, it comes with an App Quick Freeze feature so that you can easily reduce battery usage according to your convenience.
product_description.Vibrant FHD Display: This smartphone features a 16.76 cm (6.6) display with a screen resolution of up to 2408*1080 to ensure an FHD visual experience.
product_description.Powerful Unisoc Processor: The 12 nm octa-core CPU along with the Unisoc T616 processor ensures efficient performance, smooth multitasking, and more on this phone.
product_description.8.1 mm Slim Design: This smartphone comes in a lightweight design to offer an elegant appeal and style to its appearance. Also, its thickness of around 8.1 mm makes it easy to hold and carry everywhere.
